         <abstract id="aspace_ab6cfec16461fe431ccf179a4efe46a8">The collection contains photographs of Dwight Hall at Yale, which was known as the Old Library from 1889 to 1930. Included are interior and exterior views and views of the building taken during the various stages of the construction or demolition of the surrounding structures.</abstract>
    
